        "TileImage": "$($repository 103ea50a-6d9c-4c51-bf9f-0935d2c27b58).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Today we have only one target, Roberto Vargas. Roberto is known as a golf coach and local real estate agent, but in reality he uses his position to scam people into selling their homes, falsify title deeds, and take over valuable houses and land. Many victims have lost their entire fortune, except for our client&apos;s family members. The client wants revenge for all the deeds and deceptions. Good hunting 47.",
